FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[Address], [c].[CityId], [c].[CityName], [c].[CommunityId], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[CommunityTypeId], [c].[CreatedBy], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[GracePeriod], [c].[NoOfParkingLot], [c].[NoOfUnits], [c].[PICEmail], [c].[PICMobile], [c].[PICName], [c].[StateId], [c].[UpdatedBy], [c].[UpdatedDate], [s].[Id] AS [Id0], [s].[Name]
    FROM [Community] AS [c]
    LEFT JOIN [State] AS [s] ON [c].[StateId] = [s].[Id]

) AS [t]
